    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve honestly gotta see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in such incredible shape that it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! Not a single scratch, the interior is spotless, and it drives like a total dream. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home where it\u2019ll be just as loved. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 44900.0,
