    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 997.2 Carrera S represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated refinement, featuring the 3.8L MA1.01 DFI flat-six engine that eliminates previous IMS concerns while providing a linear power band. The chassis is dialed in with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and a factory-spec mechanical limited-slip differential, ensuring surgical turn-in and corner-exit traction. Every mechanical interface is in flawless state; the six-speed manual gearbox offers crisp synchromesh engagement, and the braking system features four-piston monoblock calipers over ventilated, cross-drilled rotors with zero thermal glazing. Maintained to a concours standard, the undercarriage is dry, and the ECU reveals a clean DME report with no over-rev cycles in Ranges 3-6. A turn-key, collector-grade specimen for the driver who demands mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
